@FinanceManager.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5221
@UserId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@CategoryId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@TransactionId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Criar usuario
POST {{FinanceManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Silva",
  "email": "maria.silva@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Listar usuarios
GET {{FinanceManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/users
Accept: application/json

### Criar categoria de receita
POST {{FinanceManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Salario",
  "type": 1
}

### Criar categoria de despesa
POST {{FinanceManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Moradia",
  "type": 2
}

### Listar categorias
GET {{FinanceManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Accept: application/json

### Criar transacao
POST {{FinanceManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Salario de abril",
  "amount": 3500.00,
  "date": "2026-04-07T00:00:00",
  "type": 1,
  "userId": "{{UserId}}",
  "categoryId": "{{CategoryId}}"
}

### Listar transacoes
GET {{FinanceManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/transactions
Accept: application/json

### Relatorio mensal
GET {{FinanceManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/reports/monthly?userId={{UserId}}&year=2026&month=4
Accept: application/json

### Cotacao
GET {{FinanceManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/exchangerates/latest?baseCurrency=USD&targetCurrency=BRL&amount=10
Accept: application/json
